title: viveel
author: viveel
content: Hi there.At Viveel we're launching a Beta version of our Builder this week and we are looking for testers who enjoy finding bugs we did not find yet If you are one of those guys who is king at breaking stuff and leave it at the corner so it can fix itself again (remember Sid from Toy Story?), request a seat, we are about to launch. At last you end up with a Smart Contract for free.We have limited accounts allowed so please reply or send a DM if you want a spotVisit viveel.com to know more.Join us on telegram at https://t.me/getviveel
